summary: adds a female character for cme, her body is UNP.
descriptionHtml:
This is my first mod to Skyrim and my english is not good, if you don't understand something i sorry ):

-Her body is UNP so to have a perfect Helena you have to get UNP.

-DIMONIZED UNP: http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/6709/?

-SG textures renewal(download the UNP version):http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35267/?

(her hair is from apachiiskyhair v_1_4 if you want to put other hair is your choice).
